<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Presupuesto</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --text: #222;
        --muted: #6b7280;
        --border: #e5e7eb;
        --soft: #f5f6f8;
        --dark: #2d2f34;
        --accent: #111827;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      html,
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto,
          Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans",
          sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
      }
      body {
        background: #fff;
        padding: 32px;
      }

      .page {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 24px;
      }
      .brand {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 16px;
      }
      .brand img {
        height: 48px;
        width: auto;
        object-fit: contain;
      }
      .title {
        text-align: right;
      }
      .title h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        font-size: 40px;
        color: var(--accent);
      }
      .title .number {
        margin-top: 4px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .cols {
        margin-top: 20px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
        gap: 16px;
      }
      .card {
        background: #fff;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 14px 16px;
      }
      .kv {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
        gap: 8px 16px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .kv .label {
        color: var(--muted);
      }
      .kv .value {
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .due {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 12px;
      }
      .due .label {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .due .value {
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .section-title {
        margin: 28px 0 10px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
      }
      thead th {
        background: var(--dark);
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-align: left;
        font-size: 13px;
        padding: 10px 12px;
      }
      tbody td {
        padding: 12px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        vertical-align: top;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      tbody tr:last-child td {
        border-bottom: none;
      }
      .right {
        text-align: right;
      }

      .totals {
        margin-top: 36px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px;
        gap: 16px;
      }
      .totals .summary {
        background: #fff;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 14px 16px;
      }
      .totals .row {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 6px 0;
      }
      .totals .row .label {
        color: var(--muted);
      }
      .totals .row.total {
        border-top: 1px dashed var(--border);
        margin-top: 6px;
        padding-top: 12px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .notes {
        margin-top: 32px;
      }
      .notes .label {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 13px;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      .notes .content {
        color: #4b5563;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .muted {
        color: var(--muted);
      }
      .company {
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.35;
      }
      .company strong {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: var(--accent);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="page">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="brand">
          <img src="<%= logo %>" alt="Logo" />
          <div class="company">
            <strong>GUORK VENTURES, LLC</strong><br />
            1111B S Governors Ave STE 40911. Dover, Delaware 19904, Estados
            Unidos.<br />
            https://guork.es/
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="title">
          <h1>PRESUPUESTO</h1>
          <div class="number"># <%= purchaseOrder %></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cols">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="company">
            <div class="muted" style="margin-bottom: 6px">Cobrar a:</div>
            <strong>www.wetaca.com</strong><br />
            WETACA.<br />
            NIF: B87052007<br />
            Calle de la Resina 34 - 28021 Madrid.<br />
            info@wetaca.com
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="kv">
            <div class="label">Fecha:</div>
            <div class="value"><%= issueDate %></div>
            <div class="label">Fecha de vencimiento:</div>
            <div class="value"><%= dueDate %></div>
            <div class="label">Orden de Compra:</div>
            <div class="value"><%= purchaseOrder %></div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="due"
            style="
              margin-top: 10px;
              background: var(--soft);
              border: 1px solid var(--border);
              border-radius: 8px;
              padding: 10px 12px;
            "
          >
            <div class="label">Saldo Adeudado:</div>
            <div class="value"><%= balance %></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section-title">&nbsp;</div>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Artículo</th>
            <th class="right">Cantidad</th>
            <th class="right">Tasa</th>
            <th class="right">Importe</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <strong
                >Contratación y administración de un empleado en LATAM (Tarifa
                mensual)</strong
              >
            </td>
            <td class="right"><%= quantity %></td>
            <td class="right"><%= unit %></td>
            <td class="right"><%= subtotal %></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <div class="totals">
        <div class="summary">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="label">Subtotal:</div>
            <div><%= subtotal %></div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="label">Impuesto (<%= taxRate %>%):</div>
            <div><%= taxAmount %></div>
          </div>
          <div class="row total">
            <div>Total:</div>
            <div><%= total %></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="notes">
        <div class="label">Notas:</div>
        <div class="content">
          Estamos contentos de trabajar contigo, si te encuentras interesad@,
          por favor solicitar al Account Manager el URL de Stripe para pagos con
          tarjeta de crédito o débito.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
